[http://sketchup.google.com/ Google SketchUp] is available in free and "pro" versions.  It is 3D software that allows you to share models using the [http://sketchup.google.com/3dwarehouse Google 3D Warehouse] and place them in [http://earth.google.com/ Google Earth].  It can be a useful tool for creating illustrations and models of Appropedia projects.

For some examples, see [[Rocket_Lorena_Stove#Photos_.26_Diagrams| this article]] at Appropedia.

